	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="This AD plays during the Ketheric Showdown in the lower Colony. It will play on Ketheric if Isobel is killed during the combat.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;- Load SCL_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Using ReCon command &quot;oe KethericShowdown_Start&quot;  to teleport yourself there.&#xD;&#xA;- Use command &quot;oe KethericShowdown_AudienceRoute&quot; to make sure Isobel is here, and tadpoled.&#xD;&#xA;- Go through the dialog, approach Ketheric, go through that dialog too. Combat will start.&#xD;&#xA;- To check the Apostle form version, use &quot;oe KethericShowdown_Transform&quot;.&#xD;&#xA;- Kill Isobel (either through ReCon or in-game combat). This AD will play on Ketheric." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="6" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="This AD plays during the Ketheric Showdown in the lower Colony, when the player kills Isobel during the combat. Ketheric will react to this in human form." />
			<children>
